Package comp3111.coursescraper

Class SFQ

  • java.lang.Object
    • comp3111.coursescraper.SFQ
  • public class SFQ
extends java.lang.Object
    SFQ class to store sets of SFQ information scrapped from the SFQ website. Each SFQ object contains either the course title or the instructor, as well as the SFQ score.
